metadata.name: Prayer for Ukraine
metadata.description:
Dedicated to the dead children of Ukraine. Girls, some of whom will never be brides.
Stylistically, the portrait resembles the famous Fayum portraits, and this emphasizes the idea of the horror of the victims of the war in Ukraine.
Art received a nomination in the competition Creative Photo Awards 2022 Siena, Italy.
Model - girl Nastya. Refugee from Ukraine (Cherkassy).
Size - H 10630 x W 7795 px
